nfinitys color. It is a symbolic choice which didnt come from a sudden thought, but from a design study made by our designers.<span id="more-257629"></span>At first we wanted to work on the concept of purity, introspection but also of sensibility and calm.</p>\n<p dir="ltr">As usual, during the graphic design of an idea the drafts undergo many passages and new intuitions came along with new deductions and new ways to interpret the aesthetic of a message: <strong>enhance intelligence and wisdom.</strong></p>\n<p dir="ltr">This is how our WordPress theme Libra has born. And today we release the <strong>HTML</strong> <strong>version</strong> of this powerful corporate/portfolio theme with a <strong>very large layout</strong> (<strong>1170 pixel</strong>), completely <em>responsive</em>.</p>\n<p>What are you waiting for? <strong>Download</strong> and<strong> test it</strong> immediately.</p>\n<p dir="ltr" style="text-align: center;"><a class="download-link" title="Download File" href="http://yithemes.com/?ddownload=220577&amp;ap_id=blog-theme-librahtml">Download</a><a href="http://demo.yithemes.com/html/libra/"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-38935" alt="live" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/live.png" width="241" height="64" /></a></p>\n<p dir="ltr" style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-257734" alt="001" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/001.png" width="760" height="938" /></p>\n<h2 dir="ltr">THE XHTML/CSS VERSION OF LIBRA</h2>\n<p dir="ltr">With the <strong>HTML</strong> version of <strong>Libra</strong> you can take advantage of several features: if you want to customize your homepage, you can choose among five different layouts and five slider types with whom you can compose your front page choosing your favourite slider to display your products and services.</p>\n<p dir="ltr">Libra is the perfect <strong>HTML</strong> <strong>template</strong> for a corporate/brandable site project and also for personal portfolio and blogs.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-257739" alt="021" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/021.png" width="760" height="366" /></p>\n<p dir="ltr">The <strong>XHTML/CSS</strong> template of <strong>Libra</strong> has a lots of features and a <strong>responsive</strong> <strong>layout</strong> that you can use to create and project an even more enjoyable and unique website.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-257741" alt="030" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/030.png" width="760" height="565" /></p>\n<p dir="ltr">Libra is easy to set and customize so you can create a lot of <strong>different layouts</strong> according to your needs.</p>\n<p dir="ltr">If you want, you can manually change fonts using more than <strong>600 Google Fonts</strong> and colors, so that you will have a completely changed look and style of your site.<strong> The maximum width of the template is 1170.</strong></p>\n<p dir="ltr">If you have to build your personal or company portfolio, you can choose among five different portfolio layouts, choosing the best one which fits with your needs.</p>\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>To display your work and images, you can choose among 4 different portfolio templates (Filterable,Three columns, Full description, Big image.</strong></p>\n<p dir="ltr">In the template features, there are even the blog and <strong>testimonials</strong> sections, essential for the promotion and sponsorship of your project.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-257743" alt="037" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/037.png" width="760" height="651" /></p>\n<h2 dir="ltr">CONCLUSION</h2>\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>Libra is an HTML Tempalte full of experience, from which you can take a lot</strong>.</p>\n<p dir="ltr">It belongs to the phase in which intelligence and wisdom start dominating to face the growth, to reorganize