ight="470" /></p>\n<h2 dir="ltr">GENERAL SPECIFICATIONS</h2>\n<p dir="ltr">Setting the Jewelry theme is easier thanks to the videotutorials where we explain how to configure and install the theme on your WordPress website. You can watch how to set each page of the theme step by step.</p>\n<p dir="ltr">With our advanced theme options page, you are given complete control over your theme and its settings.</p>\n<p dir="ltr">Jewelry shop is a powerful and responsive shop template, customizable according to your business requirements and needs.</p>\n<p dir="ltr" style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-222084" alt="2013-12-17_1531_001" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/2013-12-17_1531_001-1024x536.png" width="1024" height="536" /></p>\n<h2 dir="ltr">STYLE</h2>\n<p dir="ltr">In the premium version of the theme you can easily edit the colors of all the sections and elements like text, links,slogan and so on.</p>\n<p dir="ltr">You can choose Your Fonts &amp; Colors to completely customize your website:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Over 600 Google fonts  google fonts list will be automatically updated;</li>\n<li>Set font and size for titles, slogan, body text and more;</li>\n<li>Unlimited combinations of colors</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>PRODUCTS PAGE</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-222090" alt="2013-12-17_1529" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/2013-12-17_1529-1024x535.png" width="1024" height="535" /></p>\n<p dir="ltr">In the products page you can set a lot of features to organize and display your products. You can add a zoom feature in the featured image of products, on the product detail page, and you can give to users the ability to add the products in own withlist.<br />\nThanks this theme, you can allow users to compare more products of your shop in one complete table.<br />\nYou can add more tabs in the product detail image to add more features and informations about your products.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-222091" alt="2013-12-17_1530" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/2013-12-17_1530-1024x541.png" width="1024" height="541" /></p>\n<h2 dir="ltr">SLIDERS&amp;PORTFOLIO</h2>\n<p dir="ltr">You can choose among a selection of sliders and portfolios styles to compose your front page to display your products and services.</p>\n<p dir="ltr">You can create unlimited contact forms for your site and set up each form very easily by our panel.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-222096" alt="2013-12-17_1531" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/2013-12-17_1531-1024x462.png" width="1024" height="462" /></p>\n<p dir="ltr">To show your projects, you can choose among four different portfolio layouts.</p>\n<p dir="ltr" style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-222097" alt="2013-12-17_1532_002" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/2013-12-17_1532_002.png" width="875" height="349" /></p>\n<h2 dir="ltr">SHORTCODE MANAGER WITH OVER 200 SHORTCODES</h2>\n<p dir="ltr">Shortcode manager with 200+ shordcodes ready to use, to add elements on each page with just one click, without copy and paste html/css code.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Typography</strong>: quote, columns, list styles, dropcap &amp; more</li>\n<li><strong>Elements</strong>: alert boxes, buttons, tables, toggles, tabs, price tables &amp; more</li>\n<li><strong>Media</strong>: sliders, galleries, videos, images styles, lightbox</li>\n<li><strong>Shop</strong>: product sliders, credit card icons and so on</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 dir="ltr">SAMPLE DATA</h2>\n<p dir="ltr">With a simple click you can import our demo files, so your theme will appear exactly like the theme preview. You can download the HOME PSD file for our customizations.</p>\n<h2 dir="ltr">PREMIUM VERSION</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-222100" alt="2013-12-17_1532" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/2013-12-17_1532-1024x599.png" width="1024" height="599" /></p>\n<p dir="ltr">We provide free support for our premium themes, so you can open a new ticket and ask help to our developers.</p>\n<p dir="ltr">In premium version you will have a way to choose the layout for the products list in the shop page, you can add an enquiry form inside each product detail page and you can add more tabs in the products tabs of the detail page.</p>\n<p dir="ltr">In premium version you can add a popup to launch your offers, or you can use it as a palce where the users can subscribe to your newsletter list.</p>\n<p dir="ltr">With premium version you can have a new checkout layout with a multistep feature.</p>\n<h2 dir="ltr">CONCLUSIONS</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-222105" alt="2013-12-17_1531" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/2013-12-17_15311-1024x462.png" width="1024" height="462" /></p>\n<p dir="ltr">Luxury products deserve an elegant and excellent design to underline the value of your products. To achieve this goal, you can choose to download Jewelry Shop.</p>\n<p dir="ltr">What are you waiting for? Christmas is coming and you can&#8217;t miss this chance to sell your awesome products!</p>\n<p>Download it now!</p>\n<p dir="ltr" style="text-align: center;"><a class="download-link" title="Download File" href="http://yithemes.com/?ddownload=221637&amp;ap_id=blog-theme-jewerly">Download</a><a href="http://demo.yithemes.com/thejewel/"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-38935" alt="live" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/live.png" width="241" height="64" /></a></p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:90:"http://yithemes.com/blog/free-themes/jewelry-shop-e-commerce-jewelry-wordpress-theme/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xm