 had an incredible influence upon us, helping us to greet everyday life events, even the most ordinary ones, and to give them a meaning, turning events into a fruitful flux of coincidences.</p>\n<p dir="ltr" style="text-align: justify;">Our themes are always deeply inspired. But Celestino has had the prerogative of being self-imposed and to fall on our path as an important, meaningful and prophetic sign of change.</p>\n<p dir="ltr" style="text-align: justify;">The first release of November is this new, amazing and <strong>free HTML Template for your website, Celestino.<span id="more-179093"></span></strong></p>\n<p dir="ltr" style="text-align: center;"><a class="download-link" title="Download File" href="http://yithemes.com/?ddownload=179064&amp;ap_id=blog-theme-celestino">Download</a><a href="http://demo.yithemes.com/html/celestino/"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-38935" alt="live" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/live.png" width="241" height="64" /></a></p>\n<p dir="ltr" style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-179103" alt="celestino1" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/celestino1-1024x692.png" width="1024" height="692" /></p>\n<p dir="ltr">The theme has a great 1170 pixel responsive layout based on Bootstrap grid. It is clean and easy to use but even powerful and versatile. Celestino is the winning choice for corporate and portfolio websites.</p>\n<h2>THE XHTML/CSS VERSION OF CELESTINO</h2>\n<p dir="ltr" style="text-align: justify;">Celestino HTML version has several features: you can choose among 5 and more Home Page layouts, 5 and more Slider types with whom you can compose your front page choosing your favourite slider to display your product and services.</p>\n<p dir="ltr" style="text-align: justify;"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-179106" alt="celestino2" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/celestino2.png" width="966" height="772" /> <a href="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/celestino5.png"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-179107" alt="celestino5" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/celestino5-1024x457.png" width="1024" height="457" /></a> <a href="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/celestino7.png"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-179108" alt="celestino7" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/celestino7-1024x455.png" width="1024" height="455" /></a></p>\n<p dir="ltr">Furthermore, you can select five different Portfolio layouts.</p>\n<p><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-179113" alt="celestino8" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/celestino8-1024x574.png" width="1024" height="574" /></p>\n<p dir="ltr" style="text-align: justify;">To create an unique and engaging layout, you can make use of the unlimited colors choice of Celestino. In the premium version of the theme you can easily edit the colors of all the sections and elements like text, links,slogan and so on.</p>\n<p><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-179114" alt="celestino8_001" src="http://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/celestino8_001.png" width="970" height="786" /></p>\n<p dir="ltr" style="text-align: justify;">We said that nothing happens by chance. And Celestino, considering what inspired it and how it is done, surely deserves the prophetic recognition of what happens to let things change in a better way.</p>\n<p dir="ltr" style="text-align: justify;">It is a powerful theme, well projected and rich of functions and features, easy to use and ready to turn your standard website into a fascinating place of big conquests.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Now it is up to you to go on and meet the prophecy of change.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir="ltr" style="text-align: center;"><a class="download-link" title="Download File" href="http://yithemes.com/?ddownload=179064&amp;ap_id=blog-theme-celestino">Download</a><a href="http://demo.yithemes.com/html/c